research.visinator.text.stage.1=The rainbow colours and bobbing of parrots seem almost mystical to you. Maybe you can harness the energy given off by their wingflaps for magical means.
research.visinator.text.stage.2=By building on your knowledge of the Aves Alternator, you've figured out a way to exploit the magic of dancing birds to inject vis into the atmosphere.<BR>A simple construct of gold and amber strapping your Aves Alternator should, when placed beneath a mundane jukebox, provide enough power for your thaumaturgical activities.
